name: Warmup_Div02_Sub03
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD2S3.CPF,
GmailD2S3.NOME,
GmailD2S3.EMAIL,
GmailD2S3.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S3.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD2S3.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD2S3.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S3.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV02_SUB03 GmailD2S3
UNION
